질문

1. Let’s start the interview (now).

2. Tell me something about yourself.

​

답변

Wow, It’s my pleasure to tell you about me.

My name is _.

I’m _ years old.

I’ve worked _ for _ years.

​

I live in Seoul. I live with my family.

There are 4 people in my family; My parents and my sister.

I love spending time with them.

​

As for my hobby, I enjoy watching movie.

I go to the movie theater in my neighborhood.

It’s near my home, so I usually go there on the weekend.

​

Another thing I’m into is working out.

I’m trying to maintain my health.

Therefore, I go to the park for jogging and running.

Once I start jogging and running, it makes me relieve my stress.

​

This is all about me.

If you have any questions, feel free to ask me.

​

Thank you very much.

​

단어

1. pleasure

기쁨 / 즐거움 / 쾌락

2. movie theater

영화관 / 영화 극장

3. neighborhood

근처 / 인근 / 이웃 / 동네 / 이웃 사람들 / 주민 / 지역 / 지방

4. maintain

유지하다

5. therefore

그래서

6. once

~하면 / 일단

7. relive

없애주다 / 안도하게 하다 / 완화하다

​

숙어

1. as for

~에 관하여 / ~에 대하여

2. another thing

다른 것

3. working out

운동하다.

4. feel free

자유롭게

​

문법

1. have worked 일해왔다.

→ 현재완료 (have + pp) + for = 계속 적용법 → I’ve worked 마켓 for 2 years. → 나는 마켓에서 2년 동안 일해왔다. (지금도 하는 중인 것) 

2. love spending time 시간 보내는 것을 좋아하다.

→ love + 동명사 = love to + 동사 → ~ 하는 것을 좋아하다.
